{"tha-ap218:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap218:0.2":"Hatthivagga ","tha-ap218:0.3":"6 Sandhitattheraapadana ","tha-ap218:1.1":"“Assatthe haritobhase, ","tha-ap218:1.2":"samvirulhamhi padape; ","tha-ap218:1.3":"Ekam buddhagatam sannam, ","tha-ap218:1.4":"alabhimham patissato. ","tha-ap218:2.1":"Ekattimse ito kappe, ","tha-ap218:2.2":"yam sannamalabhim tada; ","tha-ap218:2.3":"Tassa sannaya vahasa, ","tha-ap218:2.4":"patto me asavakkhayo. ","tha-ap218:3.1":"Ito terasakappamhi, ","tha-ap218:3.2":"dhanittho nama khattiyo; ","tha-ap218:3.3":"Sattaratanasampanno, ","tha-ap218:3.4":"cakkavatti mahabbalo. ","tha-ap218:4.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap218:4.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap218:4.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap218:5.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma sandhito thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap218:6.1":"Sandhitattherassapadanam chattham. "}